OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,FA member of the independent commission
OL,7,Fwhich expelled Southampton from the
OL,8,Fplay-offs says accusations of bias
OL,9,Fbased on him playing a single match
OL,10,Ffor Middlesbrough are "wholly without
OL,11,Ffoundation".
OL,13,FDavid Winnie, a footballer turned
OL,14,Fsolicitor, played one match for Boro
OL,15,F33 years ago. He was part of a three-
OL,16,Fperson panel which kicked Southampton
OL,17,Fout of the play-offs for spying on a
OL,18,FMiddlesbrough training session ahead
OL,19,Fof their semi-final first leg.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
