CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,FThere has been some social media
OL,7,Fcommentary over whether that link
OL,8,Fbrought into question his independent
OL,9,Fstatus, but Winnie said it had "no
OL,10,Fbearing" on his ability to be
OL,11,Fimpartial.
OL,13,FHe said: "The suggestion that a single
OL,14,Fappearance for Middlesbrough Football
OL,15,FClub more than three decades ago could
OL,16,Fin any way influence my judgment as a
OL,17,Fmember of an independent disciplinary
OL,18,Fcommission is wholly without
OL,19,Ffoundation.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,F"My involvement with the club
OL,7,Fconsisted of one professional
OL,8,Fappearance approximately 33 years ago
OL,9,Fand has no bearing whatsoever on my
OL,10,Fability to approach these proceedings
OL,11,Fimpartially and objectively.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
