FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,F"As with all commission members, my
OL,7,Fduty was to consider only the
OL,8,Fevidence, the applicable EFL
OL,9,Fregulations, and the submissions
OL,10,Fadvanced by the parties. The decision
OL,11,Freached was unanimous and followed
OL,12,Fdetailed legal argument, documentary
OL,13,Fevidence, witness testimony and
OL,14,Fcareful deliberation by an experienced
OL,15,Findependent panel.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,F"At no stage was any issue raised by
OL,7,Feither party regarding my independence
OL,8,For suitability to sit on the
OL,9,Fcommission. Had there been any
OL,10,Flegitimate basis for concern, the
OL,11,Fappropriate procedures existed for
OL,12,Fthat to be addressed before the
OL,13,Fhearing proceeded.
OL,15,F"Professional integrity in these
OL,16,Fproceedings is paramount. My role was
OL,17,Fto uphold the integrity of the
OL,18,Fcompetition and apply the regulations
OL,19,Ffairly, without fear or favour, and
OL,20,Fthat is precisely what the commission
OL,21,Fdid."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
