PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,FThe EFL has also been approached for
OL,7,Fcomment.
OL,9,FThe commission found Southampton head
OL,10,Fcoach Tonda Eckert had authorised the
OL,11,Fspying mission at Boro, and earlier
OL,12,Fvisits to training sessions held by
OL,13,FOxford and Ipswich. The commission
OL,14,Fsaid it was "particularly deplorable"
OL,15,Fthat junior staff were delegated to
OL,16,Fcarry out the observations, with the
OL,17,Fintern caught at Boro's training
OL,18,Fsession telling the commission he felt
OL,19,Fpressured to do it.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,FWinnie, the partner and head of sports
OL,7,Fat Gilson Gray LLP, acknowledged that
OL,8,Fthe commission's decision would have
OL,9,F"serious ramifications" across
OL,10,Ffootball, but added: "The commission's
OL,11,Fduty was not to consider popularity,
OL,12,Freputation or consequence in
OL,13,Fisolation, but to uphold the integrity
OL,14,Fof the competition and apply the
OL,15,Fregulations fairly, independently and
OL,16,Fwithout fear or favour.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]rD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,F"The commission unanimously concluded
OL,7,Fthat the conduct in question
OL,8,Frepresented a deliberate and organised
OL,9,Fattempt to obtain a competitive
OL,10,Fadvantage in breach of fundamental
OL,11,Fprinciples of sporting integrity and
OL,12,Fgood faith.
OL,14,F"Football depends upon public trust.
OL,15,FSupporters, clubs, players and
OL,16,Fstakeholders must have confidence that
OL,17,Fcompetitions are conducted on a level
OL,18,Fplaying field.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779631868
OL,3,CIndependent commission member denies
OL,4,Cbias after 'Spygate' verdict
OL,6,F"This outcome reflects the seriousness
OL,7,Fwith which the commission viewed
OL,8,Frepeated breaches of the regulations,
OL,9,Fparticularly within the context of one
OL,10,Fof the most financially and
OL,11,Fcompetitively significant competitions
OL,12,Fin English football. The message is
OL,13,Fclear: cheating, in any form, has no
OL,14,Fplace in the game and will not be
OL,15,Ftolerated.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
